* [[Conrad Veidt]] as [[Cesare Borgia]]  
* [[Liane Haid]] as [[Lucrezia Borgia]]  
* [[Albert Bassermann]] as Papst [[Alexander VI|Alexander VI Rodrigo Borgia]]  
