* [[Heinrich George]] as Sebastiano  
* [[Adolf E. Licho]] as Lodowico  
* [[William Dieterle]] as [[Giovanni Sforza]], Lucrezia's impotent husband<ref>Workman, Christopher; Howarth, Troy (2016). "Tome of Terror: Horror Films of the Silent Era". Midnight Marquee Press. p. 252.{{ISBN|978-1936168-68-2}}.</ref>
* [[Lothar Müthel]] as [[Juan Borgia]]  
* [[Alphons Fryland]] as Alfonso, Prinz von Arragon 
* [[Kathe Oswald]] as Naomi  
* [[Alexander Granach]] as ein Gefangener  
* [[Anita Berber]] as Gräfin [[Giulia Farnese|Julia Orsini]]  
